Privacy Policy
This privacy policy applies to the Wildfolio app (hereby referred to as «Application») for mobile devices created by Wildfolio (hereby referred to as «Service Provider») as a Premium service. This service is provided «AS IS» without any representations or warranties, express or implied.
Information Collection, Use, and Sharing
The Application collects information when you download and use it, including:
Your device’s Internet Protocol address (IP address)
Pages visited, time and date of visit, and time spent on those pages and on the Application
The type of operating system used on your mobile device
The Application does not gather precise real-time location information from your device. However, it may collect, use, and share aggregated location data to enhance functionality and user experience, subject to the limitations described below.
Use of Google User Data
The Application accesses Google user data only with your explicit consent and solely for the purpose of AWS Cognito user registration. This allows us to associate your data generated within the app with your Google account. We adhere strictly to Google’s User Data policies and limit our use of this data to the purposes stated at the time of collection.
Your Google user data is handled as follows:
Only email adress is stored and used strictly for AWS Cognito user registration to enhance user functionality and personalization.
The permission will be granted when logging in Fluidstory app in with Google OAuth or Apple Sign in.
Stored securely and accessed only by authorized personnel.
At any point, the user can request the deletion of all their information
Third-Party Services
We engage third-party services for functionalities that enhance the Application. Here are links to the privacy policies of third-party service providers used by the Application:
Google Play Services
RevenueCat
Data Retention and Security
We retain user-provided data for as long as necessary to provide our services, and we protect it with robust physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review our policy periodically.
Your Consent
By using the Application, you consent to the processing of your data as outlined in this Privacy Policy.
Contact Us
If you have questions about our privacy practices or this Privacy Policy, please contact us via email at hello@wildfolio.me.